criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  overweight and obesity (IMC ≥ 25 using a Body Mass Analyzer TANITA-SC-330);

          -  BED (confirmed through the Eating Disorder Examination 17.0D;

          -  Access to smartphone and willingness to use it regularly (at least once a week).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  undergoing any other form of psychological intervention for BED or having attended the
             face-to-face BEfree;

          -  severe psychiatric problem (e.g., major depression; psychotic illness; bipolar
             disorder, assessed through a semi-structured interview using DSM-5 criteria).
